{"tid":1186533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拒絕「被穿高跟鞋」 日本女星連署獲2萬人支持","createTime":"2019-06-05T03:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T14:59:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5b43051c48fd3b86b40ddc3e4391f3d57cc20374","tid":1186533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nL78GvBWiqztX2kgMk1bfA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/61c71a74e3c114cfdb8374e5d0feaa0e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnL78GvBWiqztX2kgMk1bfA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2F61c71a74e3c114cfdb8374e5d0feaa0e&h=2a0a25a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼美國好萊塢METOO之後，日本寫真女星也發起「拒絕被穿高跟鞋」運動，日本職業女性因為企業的潛規則。幾乎都得穿高跟鞋上班，長期下來，輕則磨皮腳痛，嚴重的可能會重創脊椎和骨盆，這起連署活動已經獲得近2萬人支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網友推文：「穿了黑色運動鞋，被說『不是有跟的鞋就不行』，『女社員穿有跟的鞋是義務』，第一次聽到這個規則時，真的大吃一驚。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本寫真女星石川優實發起，拒絕「被穿」高跟鞋的「#KuToo運動」，因為KuToo的日文發音有苦痛之意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本職業女性一直以來都被和高跟鞋劃上等號，但這樣的潛規則卻讓女性們叫苦連天。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上班族：「腳都變紅了，回家都會儘快脫掉鞋子，每天都覺得痛，走路時這裡會磨擦，像是貼OK繃，鞋子裡面也貼一個，自己想對策。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n穿高跟鞋能讓雙腿看起來更修長，但長時間下來造成血液不流通、起水泡，甚至對脊椎、骨盆都會造成影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本寫真女星石川優實：「很多女性在職場上，或是求職時，都被要求得穿上高跟鞋，只是因為所謂的禮貌，不能脫下高跟鞋的情況讓人痛苦。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事實上美國好萊塢女星JuliaRoberts，以及「暮光女」KristenStewart，都曾在坎城影展上光腳走紅毯，為女性發聲。日本這項活動獲得近2萬人支持，也已經向日本政府提交連署請願書，盼能禁止企業強迫女員工穿高跟鞋上班，早日揮別「高跟鞋噩夢」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/拒絕-被穿高跟鞋-日本女星連署獲2萬人支持-153806412.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95-%E8%A2%AB%E7%A9%BF%E9%AB%98%E8%B7%9F%E9%9E%8B-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A5%B3%E6%98%9F%E9%80%A3%E7%BD%B2%E7%8D%B22%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81-153806412.html&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLxyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=f9cb3db4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/拒絕-被穿高跟鞋-日本女星連署獲2萬人支持-153806412.html</a>"},{"pid":"db3138517fff81e0e86df9a6745995aeba8c8367","tid":1186533,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔著鞋返工啦"},{"pid":"cfbbd48da6cde51f345d524345a6934ae4301b8b","tid":1186533,"uid":249885,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:56:41.000Z","msg":"支持 著過老母嗰對 勁奇怪"},{"pid":"637c8a334a484911bbed589335dc0eaa2f28bd2a","tid":1186533,"uid":157362,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:58:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b4a07b568e600610c9eef0295f018edc91a5c39","tid":1186533,"uid":97550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:59:04.000Z","msg":"呢件事香港 causal 好多"},{"pid":"6082739ae15f3ceeb98d1660695fd747449a0fc8","tid":1186533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1b4801c058d227d4ff627477ea9307a2f5a7ff","tid":1186533,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啊"},{"pid":"7129f5d9e474de67b0feb70db381816490690f75","tid":1186533,"uid":19501,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:26:54.000Z","msg":"平底鞋都可以好好J"},{"pid":"e29d7b9d96a83150233d151b93be0e780b66d0f2","tid":1186533,"uid":31215,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"7129f5d9e474de67b0feb70db381816490690f75","tid":1186533,"uid":19501,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:26:54.000Z","msg":"平底鞋都可以好好J"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T04:30:00.000Z","msg":"要婆仔鞋先得<br />\n嗰啲死人護士難成對地盤工程鞋咁見親都想斬撚左對腳佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm